<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="723" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="15.[1370,2576,1591,2176]" pageId="15" pageNumber="723">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1370,1608,1827,1860]" pageId="15" pageNumber="723">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but the Red-throated Squirrel is diurnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
