<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="723" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="15.[1370,2576,1591,2176]" pageId="15" pageNumber="723">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1372,1722,1985,2018]" pageId="15" pageNumber="723">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Redthroated Squirrel has a wide distribution, is common, and presents tolerance to habitat modification.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
